post_content: Back in Calvert County, at least for a little while. I realize how much crap that I have after having to move it all (again). So I'm off to do some various things this week, shopping, renew license, check up on old friends (mental note: this is important, need to make sure I do this), help my parents pack up this house, and then early friday morning leave for Massachusetts. Looking forward to that drive :).
